<br />
<br />Nestopia didn't like those NES 2.0 flags (it showed alert("Corrupt File!") and didsn't load anything), so I converted it back to iNES format by zeroing them out, and then I doubled the CHR ROM.  The garbage wasn't there in Nestopia.</div>

